outputs.text: re.sub('\W', '_', text)  # Replace special characters with '_'
re.sub(r'[^\w\s]', ' ', text)  # Replace punctuations with spaces
' '.join([c.upper() if random.choice([True, False]) else c for c in text])
re.sub(r"[^\w\s]", "", text)  # Remove all special characters
" ".join(w.upper() if random.random() < 0.5 else w for w in text.split())
" ".join(["".join([random.choice([c.lower(), c.upper()]) for c in word]) for word in text.split()])
re.sub(r"[^\w\s]", "", text).lower().strip()  # remove special characters and lowercase
text.upper() if random.choice([True, False]) else text.lower()
[t.upper() if random.random() >= 0.5 else t for t in text]
" ".join(word.upper() if random.random() >= 0.5 else word for word in text.split())
